{"tid":59301,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"數碼相機點影景（天）","createTime":"2016-12-29T14:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T14:52:57.000Z","uid":20385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb16707d8bcb17b951a5c1490acfe0c5bb18bfa0","tid":59301,"uid":20385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:08:35.000Z","msg":"今日去行山<br />\n諗住去影景 影天<br />\n試過較光圈快門曝光補償都影唔到iphone咁大對比<br />\n行申：lx10<br />\n<br />\nip:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/29/220702_d267651c717c13b537f709c0d0565a1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2F220702_d267651c717c13b537f709c0d0565a1f.jpg&h=5ab98197&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/29/220702_d0d144d819307d45acd5bf556c96117c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2F220702_d0d144d819307d45acd5bf556c96117c.jpg&h=32a51399&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaiwjHUQfhK9wvr1gBgF4E9Q9sSKUwZNUwEYD8CFZbBqp?filename=M8R0dF0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8R0dF0.jpg&h=f6e40f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相機：<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPhscciCKTPw8E2Pb5iz9dWvYqEsiTrXWXUYugA9tN9dY?filename=95KXptL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95KXptL.jpg&h=ecd0be6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fd1697b861a8126776cb1a063c1d3e38e50b398","tid":59301,"uid":14346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:11:04.000Z","msg":"基本上都係收光圈，再under少少影<br />\n自動曝光就較低-0.3 - 1個EV就差唔多"},{"pid":"d8162f2e463350f496be905e00c8173939e51aad","tid":59301,"uid":20385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本上都係收光圈，再under少少影<br />\n自動曝光就較低-0.3 - 1個EV就差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有試過<br />\n天空既對比係出左<br />\n但個景就變到好暗"},{"pid":"5c70df91588f4d8542ee3597370936bf8d5ab159","tid":59301,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"賣左部相機 用iphone影仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106b675699355dfdc25df13f13dd1ef42e638fbd","tid":59301,"uid":20385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"是味要買filter?定其實係無得救"},{"pid":"406d73983cff5c1e5bc97470b982dd1aa9a98f49","tid":59301,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:13:03.000Z","msg":"師兄意思係唔係想影出來少d光逆差？ <br />\n如果係，你可以試下用 曝光包圍，我自己會用 -2ev, -1ev, 0, +1ev, +2ev"},{"pid":"dc954976f41ace881afc6580ae81a5b6ef451576","tid":59301,"uid":14346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>基本上都係收光圈，再under少少影<br />\n自動曝光就較低-0.3 - 1個EV就差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有試過<br />\n天空既對比係出左<br />\n但個景就變到好暗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你天同地個反差太大<br />\n一係under影完，後期推高啲gamma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係HDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0463e18e2952312e0e8940694f77499356cffe","tid":59301,"uid":20385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:31:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>基本上都係收光圈，再under少少影<br />\n自動曝光就較低-0.3 - 1個EV就差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有試過<br />\n天空既對比係出左<br />\n但個景就變到好暗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你天同地個反差太大<br />\n一係under影完，後期推高啲gamma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係HDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細佬我咩都唔識 under影即係咩"},{"pid":"80020d0c45a544fd5d5aa90129bbd26e65444092","tid":59301,"uid":20385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/29/223726_38e5a84850e7a8e8883235b63b54498b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2F223726_38e5a84850e7a8e8883235b63b54498b.jpg&h=ab34c86d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n較左曝光就係咁<br />\n個天d色係好靚但個景就無晒"},{"pid":"fa496c0f3e74f58fdb66c8bc0e4c6cfbfff5b9d3","tid":59301,"uid":20385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:39:49.000Z","msg":"景同天都偏光<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfE9wFDY4aNk1gcFW52y481Kcgc1kd7fpZf6fc5KuH6Vp?filename=78wA0V0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78wA0V0.jpg&h=6dbd2303&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9915b47252666967c77dae2b271d0c2cf37da938","tid":59301,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有試過<br />\n天空既對比係出左<br />\n但個景就變到好暗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你天同地個反差太大<br />\n一係under影完，後期推高啲gamma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係HDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細佬我咩都唔識 under影即係咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔用漸變濾鏡，加降兩格灰度"},{"pid":"da855804ff29d4865efd15ff36666d396fcfc93d","tid":59301,"uid":20385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你天同地個反差太大<br />\n一係under影完，後期推高啲gamma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係HDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細佬我咩都唔識 under影即係咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔用漸變濾鏡，加降兩格灰度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是味一定要用濾鏡或者要後期製作"},{"pid":"013c9992e41af1575a6ed454399ab57abd1e9464","tid":59301,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你天同地個反差太大<br />\n一係under影完，後期推高啲gamma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係HDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細佬我咩都唔識 under影即係咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔用漸變濾鏡，加降兩格灰度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是味一定要用濾鏡或者要後期製作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?id=41925619504&amp;spm=a1z09.2.0.0.xooQKX&amp;_u=uor09jo31bf&amp;sku_properties=1627207:3232483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fid%3D41925619504%26spm%3Da1z09.2.0.0.xooQKX%26_u%3Duor09jo31bf%26sku_properties%3D1627207%3A3232483&d=iZ3UUFUrddM%2FmkppG2zdDZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=32bcf0ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?id=41925619504&amp;spm=a1z09.2.0.0.xooQKX&amp;_u=uor09jo31bf&amp;sku_properties=1627207:3232483</a>"},{"pid":"040ca46b8f887fd77d774b600af4f22e6fa29f56","tid":59301,"uid":5335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T03:40:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24e8449f6ead95df46d3e687dfcb8bd00f01ef61","tid":59301,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"本身都想答你用iphone算<br />\n因為你個問題真係好新手<br />\n我嘗試用新手角度解答<br />\n<br />\n你心裡面一定諗「嘩屌，咁多錢買部相機仲差過iphone」<br />\n而家天地光差太大，所以有地就冇天，有天就冇地<br />\niphone會自動開HDR，影一張天，一張地，一張中間再合成<br />\n所以光位暗位細節都有哂<br />\n「iphone咁勁嘅，點解我俾幾千買部相機又冇呢個功能」<br />\n因為你冇睇說明書囉懶人!<br />\n幫人幫到底，送佛送到西<br />\n幫你google埋個說明書 <br />\n<a href=\"https://eww.pavc.panasonic.co.jp/dscoi/DMC-LX10/P_PP/DMC-LX10_SQW0721_eng.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feww.pavc.panasonic.co.jp%2Fdscoi%2FDMC-LX10%2FP_PP%2FDMC-LX10_SQW0721_eng.pdf&d=iZ3UUFUrddM%2FmkppG2zdDZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8ea88111\" target=\"_blank\">https://eww.pavc.panasonic.co.jp/dscoi/DMC-LX10/P_PP/DMC-LX10_SQW0721_eng.pdf</a><br />\n方法1: P117: 影單張JPG自動壓光位推暗位，[MENU]-&gt;[REC]-&gt;[<br />\ni.Dynamic]-&gt;HIGH<br />\n方法2: P118: 影多張HDR自動合成,[MENU]&gt;[REC]&gt;[HDR]&gt;ON<br />\n<br />\n當然呢啲都係傻瓜方法，有心影相會用bracketing, raw, gnd filter，搖黑卡等等嘅方法。不過講咁多你都唔明架啦，試咗上面自動HDR先，覺得麻煩嘅都係賣咗部相機用iphone算"},{"pid":"38d7bec2014e1b03e413182ef1250755a9b2e4c8","tid":59301,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身都想答你用iphone算<br />\n因為你個問題真係好新手<br />\n我嘗試用新手角度解答<br />\n<br />\n你心裡面一定諗「嘩屌，咁多錢買部相機仲差過iphone」<br />\n而家天地光差太大，所以有地就冇天，有天就冇地<br />\niphone會自動開HDR，影一張天，一張地，一張中間再合成<br />\n所以光位暗位細節都有哂<br />\n「iphone咁勁嘅，點解我俾幾千買部相機又冇呢個功能」<br />\n因為你冇睇說明書囉懶人!<br />\n幫人幫到底，送佛送到西<br />\n幫你google埋個說明書 <br />\n<a href=\"https://eww.pavc.panasonic.co.jp/dscoi/DMC-LX10/P_PP/DMC-LX10_SQW0721_eng.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feww.pavc.panasonic.co.jp%2Fdscoi%2FDMC-LX10%2FP_PP%2FDMC-LX10_SQW0721_eng.pdf&d=iZ3UUFUrddM%2FmkppG2zdDZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8ea88111\" target=\"_blank\">https://eww.pavc.panasonic.co.jp/dscoi/DMC-LX10/P_PP/DMC-LX10_SQW0721_eng.pdf</a><br />\n方法1: P117: 影單張JPG自動壓光位推暗位，[MENU]-&gt;[REC]-&gt;[<br />\ni.Dynamic]-&gt;HIGH<br />\n方法2: P118: 影多張HDR自動合成,[MENU]&gt;[REC]&gt;[HDR]&gt;ON<br />\n<br />\n當然呢啲都係傻瓜方法，有心影相會用bracketing, raw, gnd filter，搖黑卡等等嘅方法。不過講咁多你都唔明架啦，試咗上面自動HDR先，覺得麻煩嘅都係賣咗部相機用iphone算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n串到應一應"},{"pid":"d0a264857f1c5ee8cf440dc9be3ca57615750429","tid":59301,"uid":33330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:20:51.000Z","msg":"一部Dc仔想要有幾好效果"},{"pid":"87013d33d01b82914a2fd42124dc4e4c09ce2571","tid":59301,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一部Dc仔想要有幾好效果</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線<br />\nLX10夠佢影有突啦"},{"pid":"880bf98713dd1bf84d9727bf4f9618e8bd76ebcb","tid":59301,"uid":20385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身都想答你用iphone算<br />\n因為你個問題真係好新手<br />\n我嘗試用新手角度解答<br />\n<br />\n你心裡面一定諗「嘩屌，咁多錢買部相機仲差過iphone」<br />\n而家天地光差太大，所以有地就冇天，有天就冇地<br />\niphone會自動開HDR，影一張天，一張地，一張中間再合成<br />\n所以光位暗位細節都有哂<br />\n「iphone咁勁嘅，點解我俾幾千買部相機又冇呢個功能」<br />\n因為你冇睇說明書囉懶人!<br />\n幫人幫到底，送佛送到西<br />\n幫你google埋個說明書 <br />\n<a href=\"https://eww.pavc.panasonic.co.jp/dscoi/DMC-LX10/P_PP/DMC-LX10_SQW0721_eng.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feww.pavc.panasonic.co.jp%2Fdscoi%2FDMC-LX10%2FP_PP%2FDMC-LX10_SQW0721_eng.pdf&d=iZ3UUFUrddM%2FmkppG2zdDZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8ea88111\" target=\"_blank\">https://eww.pavc.panasonic.co.jp/dscoi/DMC-LX10/P_PP/DMC-LX10_SQW0721_eng.pdf</a><br />\n方法1: P117: 影單張JPG自動壓光位推暗位，[MENU]-&amp;gt;[REC]-&amp;gt;[<br />\ni.Dynamic]-&amp;gt;HIGH<br />\n方法2: P118: 影多張HDR自動合成,[MENU]&amp;gt;[REC]&amp;gt;[HDR]&amp;gt;ON<br />\n<br />\n當然呢啲都係傻瓜方法，有心影相會用bracketing, raw, gnd filter，搖黑卡等等嘅方法。不過講咁多你都唔明架啦，試咗上面自動HDR先，覺得麻煩嘅都係賣咗部相機用iphone算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}